<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/122376917-colin-b"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1630834210i/122376917._UX100_CR0,16,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
