<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/122376917-colin-b">Colin B.</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">go to amazon website, look for the book, and click on &quot;kindle version&quot;. Then click &quot;buy with one-click&quot;. Turn on your kindle, turn off airplane mode a<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">go to amazon website, look for the book, and click on "kindle version". Then click "buy with one-click". Turn on your kindle, turn off airplane mode and wait a minute. Voila, there it will be.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
